The app is easy to use, but takes a little bit to learn how to use it so this is the guide of how to use for new users. 1. Exit the stardew app but leave it running in the background 2. Open Save Editor and select the current time. *Heads up: the game will open at the beginning of the day if you do this in game at 6 - 7:30 am* 3. Make the edits and add what you need, save in the upper right corner. 4. Cose both apps and reopen game and reload save. It will erase the edits if you skip this.
